articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About Me
My name is Marco Tchernychev, I go to Brookline High School.
About the Project
My project, The Fuel Efficiency of cars, compares the fuel efficiency of cars to their weight.
Goals
Educate people on how to be more environmentally conscious.
A complication for this goal is that it might be difficult to get this graphic shown to enough people.

Practice my R Studio skills!
“This is data science”
Preceptor

Kane’s Free Data Science High School Bootcamp
